# API conventions

- Prisma models: User, Group, GroupMember, Round, Leg
- One leg per user per round (`@@unique([roundId, userId])`)
- Round auto-locks when `legs.length >= group.members.length`
- Settlement updates GroupMember points, User totals, and round P/L
- Use transactions for multi-table settlement updates when extending
